cona termo aislantes fácilmente desmontables para una limpieza fácil e higiénica. También cuenta con una tapa de vidrio templado resistente a los golpes y una rejilla adaptada que le permitirá mantener la temperatura de los alimentos mientras el resto se cocinan."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Cast aluminium wok with a high quality and PFOA-free TEFLON® PLATINUM PLUS inner and outer non-stick coating."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Suitable for all types of cookers, including induction cookers."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Wok en fonte d'aluminium avec revêtement antiadhésif intérieur et extérieur TEFLON® PLATINUM PLUS haut de gamme et sans PFOA."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Adapté à toutes les plaques de cuisson, y compris les plaques à induction."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"CD"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"AD"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"MA"},{"id":"Calificacion6","type":"STRING","value":"ES"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"14"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"206","id_Ext":"347187090","value":"g"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"213","id_Ext":"347188090","value":"ml"}]},{"id":"ColoresYTallas","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"ColorFabricante","type":"STRING","value":"NEGRO"},{"id":"Tallas","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"393","id_Ext":"2416794090","value":"Wok de 32 cm"},{"id":"TamanoHorma","type":"STRING","value":"32 CM"},{"id":"Dibujo","type":"STRING","value":"INDUCCION"}]},{"id":"Variantes","type":"GROUPING","children